txt.en: 'My travels have taken me through much of Middle-earth.'
'I have been treated with the greatest respect by both Elves and dwarves here in Ered Luin.'
'There are many beautiful Elf-ruins in Ered Luin, but be wary of wild animals if you visit them.'
'The wind that comes down from the mountains can be bitingly cold. Dress warmly if you travel north!'
'Looks like you had a good haul today, friend.'
